{{zh-forms|[[东]][[西]]|[[東西]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: dōngxī

====Etymology====
Literally, the two [[morpheme]]s that compose this word mean ''east'' and ''west''

===Noun===
'''dōngxī'''
# [[east]] snd [[west]], from east to west.

===Noun===
'''dōngxi''' 
# [[something]]; [[thing]]

===Notes===
*'''东西''' means thing in a physical sense, whereas [[事情]] means thing in an abstract sense.

